parameter.description:
The Uncalibrated Echo Response (UER) [a(0),b(0)], [a(1),b(1)], ...
{{list|with each list item consisting of the following}}
{{datatype|expand}}
The value of UER at frequency i*{{param|UERGroupSize}}*Df = ({{param|UERScaleFactor}}/(2^31))*(a(i)+j*b(i))/(2^31) where Df = 4.3125 kHz.
This parameter is defined as CPE SELT uncalibrated echo response (SELT-UER-R) in ITU-T Recommendation {{bibref|G.996.2|Clause A.2.2.1}}.

